# Build context is the repo root; this image only needs the .NET source under src/
# (core, agentruntime, workflows, api). Everything below is excluded from the upload
# tar so the ACR build context stays small.
#
# NOTE: patterns are intentionally written WITHOUT a trailing slash. az acr build's
# ignore matcher did not honor `dir/`-style (trailing-slash) patterns here, so the
# whole context (~640MB) used to upload and the build hung. Plain `dir` form works.

# Frontend app — not part of the API image (its node_modules/.next are ~650MB).
src/web

# .NET build artifacts — the container runs a fresh restore/publish.
**/bin
**/obj

# Node / build outputs (anywhere they appear)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist

# VCS / agent worktrees / IDE / infra / docs — not needed in the image.
.git
.gitignore
.claude
.claire
.vs
.vscode
*.user
infra
.github
plans
**/TestResults
.monday_tkn
